              <p class="micro">I love collaborating on web and cloud projects, mentoring new developers and designing delightful UIs. Tell me about your idea ‚Äî I‚Äôm curious!</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-cards">
            <div class="info-card">
              <div class="info-row">üìß <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jyoti24703@gmail.com">jyoti24703@gmail.com</a></div>
              <div class="info-row">üìû <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+919876543210">+91-9876543210</a></div>
              <div class="info-row">üìç <strong>Location:</strong> New Delhi, India</div>
            </div>

            <div class="social-card">
              <p class="small">Find me on</p>
              <div class="socials">
                <a href="https://github.com/jyoti24703-netizen" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jyoti-yadav-043b56320/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stay in the loop -->
            <div class="newsletter-card">
              <p class="small">Stay in the loop</p>
              <div class="stay-loop">
                <input id="stayEmail" type="email" placeholder="Your email" />
                <button id="stayBtn" class="subscribe" disabled>
